- "admins who have been charged for late DVD returns" refers to users with role = 'admin' and fine_amount > 0.0; 
- "accessed after 2022" is determined by the access date being greater than the year 2022; 
- "checked-out DVDs with fines" refers to items with access_type = 'check out' or 'view' and fine_amount > 0.0.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT barcode 
FROM items
WHERE isbn IS NOT NULL;

